reviewText: I like Jesse Duplantis.  This is a great series to encourage you in your faith, as well as remind you to laugh along the way.  God has a sense of humor, so why shouldn't we?  Can't wait to watch all of it...

Brother Jesse Duplantis continues with his series of excerpts from many sermons based on his hilarious life experiences. This is good clean humor with a Godly message here and there- wonderful Christian entertainmentand ministry too.
